http://www.thehindu.com/news/cities/Vijayawada/Kalyan-Jewellers-expands-footprint-in-State/article14001004.ece

Kalyan Jewellers announced the transformation of its 26 ‘My Kalyan’ customer service outlets across the State into mini diamond stores to make diamonds available to all households.These stores will offer Kalyan’s exquisite range of diamond jewellery including earrings, pendants, necklaces, rings and nose pins with costs ranging from Rs. 8,000 to Rs. 25,000. “Our popular range of diamonds will break the myth that diamonds are ‘expensive’ and ‘exclusive’. They are expected to contribute Rs. 100 crore in the new financial year,” Kalyan Jewellers chairman and managing director T.S. Kalyanaraman stated in a press release.